=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Company => Str

An identifier for the company that manages a specific security
standard. For existing standards, the value is equal to C<Amazon Web
Services>.


=head2 Product => Str

An identifier for the product that manages a specific security
standard. For existing standards, the value is equal to the Amazon Web
Services service that manages the standard.



